data.description: MUST SEE! Gorgeous, new 2022 manufactured home with 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms in Ocala! Master bedroom with storage space and walk-in closet. Large, cleared backyard of over 0.23+ acres of private land. You own the lot, no lot rent. NO HOA! Home has well, septic, and is in a GREAT LOCATION! Close by to the famous World Equestrian Center, Downtown Ocala, Williston, Gainesville, I-75, restaurants, farms, shopping and more. Seller financing available! Do not wait, it will not last long!
